events.description:
Come join us for this FREE Seminar on NAV 2015 update where you will get to learn how Microsoft Dynamics NAV can help your business grow! Get a glimpse of Microsoft Dynamics NAV testdrive now: 
http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics/erp-nav-overview.aspx 
27th March 2015 (Friday) Microsoft Singapore 1 Marina Boulevard, #22-01 Auditorium, One Marina Boulevard, Singapore 018989. 

CyanSYS Pte Ltd would like you to take this opportunity to show how Microsoft Dynamics NAV 2015 gives a complete control over your core business processes to perfect your supply chain and growth in business. Let us show you how Microsoft Dynamics NAV can help you turn insights into actions. 
Why Microsoft Dynamics NAV? 

Streamlines Financial Practices; 
Gets a clear view of your financials;
Provides self-service reporting tools and real-time business intelligence;
Identifies and target your top customers to drive new sales opportunities;
Delivering superior customer service with effective service order management;
Build customer loyalty with customer-specific pricings and discounts;
Conduct business internationally;
Connect your remote and roaming employees;
Simple to learn to use;
Drives value for your business.

Agenda for the event include: 
0930 – Registration 1000 – Accelerating your growth with CyanSYS Pte Ltd 1015 – Enhance your productivity with Microsoft Dynamics NAV 2015 1115 – Tea Break 1130 – Don't Miss these Promotions!!! 1145 – Networking Session 1200 – End of Seminar  Invest half a day to see how Microsoft Dynamics NAV 2015 can help you in your business today.  We look forward to seeing you at our event. 
Do visit our website at www.cyansys.com to know more about us.
